replies.body:
{{champion:267}} 
Nami is my favorite support right now. She is fun, effective, and has a lot of utility. She isn't as hard as people make her out to be, but it'll take a while to get the hang of her Aqua Prison. I highly recommend playing her. She is pretty compared to other champions base speed as well, so that helps with the problem of her being squishy. I like to play her super aggressive early and it usually works out, so I wouldn't worry about that. 
---
